{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_55","type":"agent_message","text":"The remaining gaps are coming from the Woodstox class hierarchy that `StaxBridge` reflects over: `EntityDecl` for `getName`, `ExtEntity` for the URI/public-id accessors, and `UnparsedExtEntity` as the concrete runtime type. I’m adding the `ExtEntity` accessors in the same conditioned block so the next trace run covers the full inheritance chain instead of walking it one method at a time."}}
